	
	README			GENEsYs 1.0, Ba, 02.Jul.92

==============================================================================

	This directory contains the documentation of GENEsYs 1.0 as LaTeX
	as well as postscript version.  To rebuild the documentation, you
	should type
			make dvi
			make dvi

	(two times !).
	If you follow the instructions given  in the documentation on ex-
	tending the software by additional test functions, the documenta-
	tion will be kept up-to-date each time you run the makefile.
